      <title>用hexo建立自己的GitPages博客</title>
      <link href="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/"/>
      <url>/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Preparation"><a href="#Preparation" class="headerlink" title="Preparation"></a>Preparation</h1><ul><li>GitHub注册账号（本例中CoderMonkie）</li><li>Nodejs安装（本例中Win64环境）</li><li>编辑工具（本文使用Visual Studio Code）</li></ul><h1 id="1-Create-a-repository-on-GitHub"><a href="#1-Create-a-repository-on-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="1. Create a repository on GitHub"></a>1. Create a repository on GitHub</h1><p>在注册好的GitHub网站，点New，创建新的Repository。<br>填写Reposition名即网站名，格式为[你的用户名].github.io，如：<br>CoderMonkie.github.io</p><a id="more"></a><p>选择Public，初始化带readme文件，ignore可不选，版权信息可不选。</p><p><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2018-12-31_201614.jpg" alt="create-repository-0"><br><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2018-12-31_201816.jpg" alt="create-repository-1"><br><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2018-12-31_201825.jpg" alt="create-repository-2"></p><h1 id="2-Install-hexo"><a href="#2-Install-hexo" class="headerlink" title="2. Install hexo"></a>2. Install hexo</h1><p>安装hexo</p><ul><li><p>自己找个路径新建一个文件夹（本例中CoderMonkeyBlog），在该路径下，用npm命令初始化</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmd">npm init<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样，就创建出package.json文件，然后就可以安装hexokinase了</p><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmd">npm install -g hexo-cli <br>hexo version<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过查看版本看是否安装成功。</p></li><li>Edit [_config.yml] 修改配置文件<br>主要修改以下Site，Url，Deployment，照实填写即可</li></ul><h1 id="3-Use-hexo-to-create-a-new-post"><a href="#3-Use-hexo-to-create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="3. Use hexo to create a new post"></a>3. Use hexo to create a new post</h1><p>使用hexo发布文章</p><ul><li>创建一篇文章<figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bat">hexo new post "hexoBlogGitPages"<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>由此在source/_posts文件夹下生成“hexoBlogGitPages.md”的markdown文件，<br>编辑此文件内容，就是你要发布的文章内容。语法自行百度markdown。  </p><h1 id="4-先在本地查看生成的结果"><a href="#4-先在本地查看生成的结果" class="headerlink" title="4. 先在本地查看生成的结果"></a>4. 先在本地查看生成的结果</h1><p>用generate命令，生成文件<br><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bat">hexo g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2018-12-31_233018.jpg" alt="hexo generate"></p><p>再用serve命令，启动localhost<br><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bat">hexo s<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2018-12-31_233114.jpg" alt="hexo serve"></p><p>这时候查看该 <a href="http://localhost:4000/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000/</a><br>地址就能看到发布后的博客效果了。（没有问题的话下一步就是发布到GitPages上）</p><h1 id="5-部署到GitPages上"><a href="#5-部署到GitPages上" class="headerlink" title="5. 部署到GitPages上"></a>5. 部署到GitPages上</h1><p>安装 hexo-deployer-git<br><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bat">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>如果配置没有改好的话，此时修改配置文件[_config.yml]<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs undefined">deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repo: git@github.com:CoderMonkie/CoderMonkie.github.io.git<br>  branch: master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>配置好之后，clean命令清除站点文件，deploy命令重新生成站点文件并推送到github指定的库上<br><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bat">hexo clean<br>hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2018-12-31_233114.jpg" alt="hexo clean"></p><p>clone时用的ssh，配置文件里相应的填了ssh的repo的url，<br>出以下问题：(没有访问权限，验证失败)<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs undefined">Host key verification failed.<br>fatal: Could not read from remote repository.<br><br>Please make sure you have the correct access rights<br>and the repository exists.<br>FATAL Something&apos;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: http://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html<br>Error: Host key verification failed.<br>fatal: Could not read from remote repository.<br><br>Please make sure you have the correct access rights<br>and the repository exists.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>查了下没有解决，直接改成https然后重新clone的。<br>（Clone的不一样了，需要修改配置里的repo）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs undefined">deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repo: https://github.com/CoderMonkie/CoderMonkie.github.io.git<br>  branch: mater<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>重新做了一遍然后执行[hexo deploy]，挣扎了几秒后就成功了。<br><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/201901-01_021414.jpg" alt="hexo deploy"></p><h1 id="6-View-the-site"><a href="#6-View-the-site" class="headerlink" title="6. View the site"></a>6. View the site</h1><p>查看博客发布后的结果<br><a href="https://codermonkie.github.io/">https://codermonkie.github.io/</a><br><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2019-01-01_020856.jpg" alt="blog-1"><br><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2019-01-01_020909.jpg" alt="blog-2 with picture"></p><hr><h1 id="添加图片的办法"><a href="#添加图片的办法" class="headerlink" title="添加图片的办法"></a>添加图片的办法</h1><ol><li>修改配置文件：</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs undefined">post_asset_folder: true<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>hexo目录下安装：hexo-asset-image</li></ol><figure class="highlight bat"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bat">npm install hexo-asset-image --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>创建文章时，会自动在_post目录下创建与md文件名相同的文件夹，引用图片的md文件中如下<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs md">![<span class="hljs-string">image-title</span>](<span class="hljs-link">foldername/imagename</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><p><img src="/2018/12/31/hexoBlogGitPages/2019-01-01_020934.jpg" alt="add image"></p>]]></content>
      
      
